00:21:14.610 --> 00:21:19.530
Mendeleev is the one who taught us
that the properties of the elements

00:21:19.530 --> 00:21:24.330
are a function of the atomic mass.
So let's get that down.

00:21:24.330 --> 00:21:28.990
By the way, the Cyrillic to Latin
translation has not been agreed upon,

00:21:28.990 --> 00:21:33.660
so you will see Mendeleev's name
