00:44:36.990 --> 00:44:40.710
has been reported.
Obviously it has to be heavy.

00:44:40.710 --> 00:44:44.420
All the light ones have been
discovered. The new ones are going

00:44:44.420 --> 00:44:48.140
to be heavy, so that's great
reporting. The element tentatively

00:44:48.140 --> 00:44:52.130
named administratium.
It has been tentatively named

00:44:52.130 --> 00:44:56.390
administratium.
And this will have to go up before

00:44:56.390 --> 00:45:00.660
The International Union of Pure and
